last_episode_to_air.name: The Boulet Brothers' Dragula: Titans Grand Finale
last_episode_to_air.overview: In this finale episode, only the strongest monsters of the cast remain alive with one final chance to prove their power before the Boulet Brothers can determine who will win the grand prize and become the first Titan of The Boulet Brothers' Dragula.

name: The Boulet Brothers' Dragula: Titans
overview: This spin-off series features drag icons from the main show’s previous seasons. They will compete in a grand championship of drag artistry and physical challenges for a $100,000 grand prize, along with the headlining spot on the upcoming world tour and the first ever Dragula Titans crown and title.

episodes.name: Halloween House Party
episodes.overview: Welcome to the Underworld! The returning drag monsters are challenged to create looks fit for a Halloween House Party in Hell on this premiere episode. Special guest judges Cassandra Peterson (Elvira) and Justin Simien join hosts, the Boulet Brothers, on the panel.

episodes.name: Revenge of the Witch
episodes.overview: The Boulet Brothers have one last terrifying trick up their sleeves for the competitors to celebrate the Halloween Season. The monsters left alive are tasked with creating witch-inspired looks, but not before surviving a witch trial that leaves some serious burns.

episodes.name: Science-Fiction (Horror) Double Feature
episodes.overview: The competition is heating up as The Boulet Brothers send the remaining drag monsters to the depths of space for this episode's Science-Fiction Horror challenge. While the competitors are tasked with creating looks fit for deep space travel, they must also navigate the alliances and rivalries forming amongst each other or face elimination.

episodes.name: Dungeons and Drag Queens Two: Into the Underdark
episodes.overview: The monsters must delve deeper into the catacombs and prepare fantasy inspired looks and performances in this episode's Dungeons and Drag Queens challenge. As tensions flare, the competitors must work together to escape the Boulet Brothers' Underdark Maze or have their fates sealed in the expansion of this returning challenge.

episodes.name: Zombie Prom
episodes.overview: The Boulet Brothers push the competitors out of their comfort zones as they are tasked with transforming basic and pretty drag looks ready for prom, into shambling members of the living dead for a two-part challenge from hell.

episodes.name: The Ugly Ladies of Wrestling Rematch!
episodes.overview: Let's get ready to rumble! The Boulet Brothers have tasked the remaining competitors to create wrestling looks and choreograph a tag-team match of bone-crushing proportions.

episodes.name: Sea Monsters of the Depths
episodes.overview: In this week's episode, the monsters find themselves in dark water for this week's Sea Monster challenge while trying to avoid an early burial at sea.

episodes.name: Horror Icons Reanimated
episodes.overview: With only one challenge left to determine the season's finalists, the monsters are tasked with creating looks inspired by some of the Horror genre's most iconic characters.

episodes.name: The Boulet Brothers' Dragula: Titans Grand Finale
episodes.overview: In this finale episode, only the strongest monsters of the cast remain alive with one final chance to prove their power before the Boulet Brothers can determine who will win the grand prize and become the first Titan of The Boulet Brothers' Dragula.
